1
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:40,560
Young man,

2
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:42,320
don't be ungrateful.

3
00:00:42,480 --> 00:00:44,080
For this girl to marry the Mountain God

4
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:45,210
is her good fortune.

5
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,650
Just think about it.

6
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:48,360
What is the God's status,

7
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,560
and what is hers?

8
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:51,080
You are all being deceived.

9
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,680
Your so-called Mountain God

10
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:55,080
is nothing but a demon from the Underworld.

11
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:55,920
He is a demon,

12
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:56,800
not a god.

13
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,560
You are the one talking nonsense!

14
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:01,240
If he weren't a god, how could he conjure up so much food for us?

15
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,300
If he weren't a god,

16
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:05,200
how would he know to come and save us from our suffering?

17
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,730
The suffering in this world

18
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:10,039
is caused by rampaging demons in the first place.

19
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:11,920
They are the creators of suffering.

20
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:14,640
Of course they know what kind of lives you are living.

21
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,560
Not this again.

22
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,200
They are exactly the same

23
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,400
as the people who came before.

24
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:18,800
Right.

25
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:20,200
Trying to brainwash us.

26
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,400
Do you think we are fools?

27
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,520
People like you

28
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:25,210
are merely nourishment for the Mountain God.

29
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:27,039
I am not brainwashing you.

30
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:29,120
I am telling you the truth.

31
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:29,980
Wuzhou.

32
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,650
I'll just ask you one thing.

33
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,920
Did you sacrifice all the cultivators who came before

34
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,920
to the Mountain God?

35
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,320
That is their good fortune.

36
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:47,680
Yes.

37
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:48,320
Good fortune.

38
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:48,560
Right.

39
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:53,560
Good fortune.

40
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,120
You...

41
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,050
Brother Wuzhou.

42
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,770
Brother Wuzhou.

43
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,520
Sister Mu.

44
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:01,880
I finally found you.

45
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,120
Why are you here?

46
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,490
Where is Li Yuan?

47
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,640
Danyu.

48
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,800
I'm glad you're okay.

49
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,040
Brother Li

50
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:18,160
is in a stalemate with the Nether Demon.

51
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,810
As for these villagers,

52
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:23,840
they...

53
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:24,880
They...

54
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,480
Sister Mu,

55
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,690
you're injured.

56
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,400
My injury is fine.

57
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:31,760
Wuzhou.

58
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:34,400
You don't need to make excuses for them.

59
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:36,500
The facts are right in front of us.

60
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,600
Even if they were innocent once,

61
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,020
things have completely changed now.

62
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,890
These villagers

63
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,040
were bewitched.

64
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,760
They became the Dark Demon's minions long ago,

65
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:49,079
aiding and abetting him.

66
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,480
The previous cultivators

67
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,880
also walked right into the trap.

68
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,140
And they planned to...

69
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,160
What?

70
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,600
How could they do this?

71
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,600
As expected of the God and Demon World,

72
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,320
the people here are indeed fierce.

73
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,920
Since the facts are settled,

74
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,080
we might as well think about

75
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,810
how to get through this crisis.

76
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:06,840
Brother Wuzhou,

77
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,640
Sister Mu,

78
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,840
since they have already aided the enemy,

79
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,440
then we...

80
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,240
can we just ignore them?

81
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:15,760
I mean,

82
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,720
should we go help the Demon...

83
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,340
Brother Li,

84
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,650
and deal with the Dark Demon together?

85
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:22,840
You're right.

86
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,530
Let's go.

87
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,200
My Lord,

88
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,560
since you have escaped the seal,

89
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,329
why didn't you return to Lanqi,

90
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:41,210
summon the demon army to launch a counterattack,

91
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:44,060
but instead, stay here with these cultivators?

92
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,640
Have you forgotten

93
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:49,040
how the human race treated you?

94
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,760
Someone like you

95
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,880
isn't even worthy of being my dog.

96
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:53,280
You!

97
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,920
What a piece of trash,

98
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,980
you can't even stop a few sacrifices.

99
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:05,120
Lanqi Moyuan,

100
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,800
do you really think

101
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,330
you are still the Demon Lord you once were?

102
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,770
Having been sealed for so long,

103
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,400
I don't believe

104
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:17,560
you can still cover the sky with one hand.

105
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,570
I didn't expect that

106
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:43,980
I still couldn't defeat you even when you're this weak.

107
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,040
I said,

108
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,800
someone like you

109
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,040
will never be worthy of being my dog.

110
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:49,440
You!

111
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,880
In that case,

112
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,760
then I will...

113
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,120
Oh no.

114
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,440
He is absorbing the villagers' life force.

115
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:14,920
Wuzhou.

116
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,490
Let's do something to help Brother Li too.

117
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,400
Lord Mountain God,

118
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,200
please have mercy!

119
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,240
Don't abandon us.

120
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:30,240
We will double our offerings of nourishment.

121
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,600
My Lord.

122
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,760
Didn't they say I know magic too?

123
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,220
But how on earth do I use it?

124
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,280
Pure blood.

125
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,080
The purest source blood.

126
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,080
So that's how it is.

127
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,000
You actually found

128
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,440
Lanqi.

129
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,440
Stop us?

130
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,960
Do you think you can still

131
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,620
stop us in your current state?

132
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:57,600
This damn Nether Demon

133
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,400
wants to drag us down with him before he dies.

134
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,360
Calling out Lanqi and Moyuan's names right now,

135
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,220
does he want us all to be wiped out?

136
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,520
You are injured.

137
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,520
Yiyi,

138
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,720
you are finally awake.

139
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:13,320
I sensed your consciousness was very chaotic,

140
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,840
as if you were in danger.

141
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,240
That Nether Demon

142
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,240
couldn't wait to suck us dry.

143
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:22,010
Do you think that's dangerous?

144
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:38,720
So you were protecting them.

145
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,320
Oh no.

146
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,440
The Child of the World is in danger.

147
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,120
The Child of the World is in danger.

148
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,520
Nothing can happen to him now.

149
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:45,600
Otherwise, both of us will be in big trouble.

150
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,600
What should we do?

151
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,290
Go stand in front of him.

152
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,360
I will use my energy to create a barrier.

153
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,960
I'll do my best.

154
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,680
Stupid woman.

155
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,560
How

156
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,240
could he?

157
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,400
Go.

158
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,360
Grandpa,

159
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,160
can I not go?

160
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,320
Ayuan.

161
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:57,680
No.

162
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,400
The underground riot

163
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,860
is getting out of control.

164
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:01,680
You must

165
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,520
grow up quickly.

166
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,920
Grandpa,

167
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,240
I'm afraid of the pain.

168
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:10,730
Even if it hurts,

169
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,040
you must endure it.

170
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,600
Once you become strong,

171
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,860
it won't hurt anymore.

172
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,480
Go.

173
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:19,800
Go.

174
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:24,520
The Netherworld is about to open.

175
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,040
You have to survive,

176
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,160
A'yuan.

177
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,440
Are these

178
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,400
his memories?

179
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,970
The greatest demon of the Netherworld

180
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:37,080
was actually raised by humans.
